<HEADLINE> UN Envoy on Mission to Reduce Afghan-Iran Tension </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, October 8 (Xinhua) -- U.N. Special Envoy on
Afghanistan Lakhdar Brahimi arrived here from Tehran Thursday
night on the second leg of his visit to the region to try to
reduce prevailing tension between Iran and Afghanistan.
</P>
