<HEADLINE> Primakov: Russia Remains World Player </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, October 8 (Xinhua) -- Russia is still an active player
on the international arena despite current hardship, Russian Prime
Minister Yevgeny Primakov said here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
After meeting with visiting Palestinian Leader Yasser Arafat
Primakov told reporters that "Despite the tough times Russia is
suffering, we continue playing an active role on the international
arena."
</P>
<P>
