its role is positive. Russia's role "is aimed at achieving
stability, settling conflicts peacefully, and establishing a just
peace in all the regions of the globe," he said.
</P>
<P>
On the Middle East policy, Primakov said Russia supports
"Palestinian demands for a just peace which will create all
conditions for normalization and a normal existence of all peoples
inhabiting this region, instead of bringing about a settlement in
the interest of one against the other."
</P>
<P>
Referring to the settlement of the Turkey-Syria standoff, he
said Russia was using diplomatic channels to remove tension in
relations between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
"We are watching this situation attentively and doing
everything through diplomatic channels to ease tension," Primakov
said. 
