Rovers), Regis Rotenbuehler (Neuchatel Xamax), Ramon Vega
(Tottenham), Stefan Wolf (Servette), Johann Vogel (Grasshoppers),
Ciriaco Sforza (Kaiserslautern), Raphael Wicky (Werder Bremen),
Patrick Mueller (Servette); Stephane Chapuisat (Borussia
Dortmund), David Sesa (Lecce).
</P>
