described his meeting with President Assad as satisfactory and
constructive.
</P>
<P>
Asked about his assessment of the Syrian-Turkish problem,
Karrazi said there were appropriate grounds for its solution,
expressing hope that a practical settlement will be found.
</P>
<P>
