bullion in Sydney closed at 300.35 U.S. dollars an ounce, down
from 301.60 U.S. dollars Thursday.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 318.21 million stocks traded for 958.66
million Australian dollars (590.34 million U.S. dollars), with
falling stocks outnumbering rising stocks 596 to 455, while 367
stocks remained steady.  
