<HEADLINE> Ukraine Calls for Peaceful Settlement to Kosovo Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, October 8 (Xinhua) -- Ukrainian President Leonid Kuchma
said Thursday his country is willing to participate as a mediator
in efforts to peacefully solve the Kosovo crisis.
</P>
<P>
At a meeting with Foreign Minister Boris Tarasyuk, Kuchma
expressed his concern over the developments in Kosovo, saying that
the only way to solve the crisis is to start peaceful talks
immediately.
</P>
<P>
