meeting on security and other issues in the region, especially
situation in the Yugoslav province of Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
The six countries are Greece, Romania, Bulgaria, Albania,
Yugoslavia and Turkey, the English newspaper Daily News said
Friday.
</P>
<P>
